The following general-purpose ACDC credential schemas were retained from the
source and may be further evolved here:

  gcd, ai-coder, ai-user-coca, attestation, award, bindkey, citation,
  dossier-base, faa, face-to-face, org-vet, proof-of-control

Telco- and vLEI-specific credential types from the source were intentionally
removed and are not part of this fork.
